"how to create a console command. This article covers how to use a console"
" command directly from your controller."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../console/command_in_controller.rst:11
msgid ""
"You may have the need to execute some function that is only available in "
"a console command. Usually, you should refactor the command and move some"
" logic into a service that can be reused in the controller. However, when"
" the command is part of a third-party library, you wouldn't want to "
"modify or duplicate their code. Instead, you can execute the command "
"directly."
msgstr ""

